wind up someplace called...</i>

91
00:18:18,222 --> 00:18:19,932
<i>Not Furya.</i>

92
00:18:28,982 --> 00:18:32,194
<i>Yet again, someone was 
trying to play me.</i>

93
00:18:34,655 --> 00:18:36,156
<i>So yet again,</i>

94
00:18:38,617 --> 00:18:40,452
