<i>Somewhere along 
the way, I lost a step.</i>

98
00:20:27,643 --> 00:20:29,478
<i>I got sloppy.</i>

99
00:20:30,062 --> 00:20:31,939
<i>Dulled my own edge.</i>

100
00:20:33,899 --> 00:20:37,027
<i>Maybe I went and did the 
worst crime of all...</i>

101
00:20:38,612 --> 00:20:40,739
<i>I got civilized.</i>

102
00:20:47,537 --> 00:20:50,374
<i>So now we zero the clock.</i>

103
00:20:52,251 --> 00:20:55,629
