no-name world.</i>

104
00:20:58,423 --> 00:21:01,051
<i>Gotta find that 
animal side again.</i>

105
00:22:37,105 --> 00:22:42,319
<i>Before long, I realized there was 
a whole other world over there,</i>

106
00:22:43,403 --> 00:22:46,490
<i>of water, grass and life.</i>

107
