I repeat, there is no reason for you 
to land at this location at this time.

147
00:39:16,437 --> 00:39:17,688
<i>Is that clear?</i>

148
00:39:17,730 --> 00:39:21,859
<i>No reason for you to land at 
this location at this time.</i>

149
00:39:24,403 --> 00:39:26,614
What the fuck did I just say?

150
