Well, this is a co-op station, 
pal. It's open to all Mercs.

166
00:40:42,606 --> 00:40:45,192
- By the way, my name is... 
- "Too late."

167
00:40:45,359 --> 00:40:48,362
That's your name. "Too Late."

168
00:40:49,196 --> 00:40:51,907
And I don't need you stepping all 
over my dick here, my friend.

169
00:40:52,992 --> 00:40:54,869
Well, I'll tell you what.

170
00:40:55,703 --> 00:40:59,957
I won't lift a finger to help until 
you come ask me for it. How's that?

171
