calling a taxi.

180
00:41:41,332 --> 00:41:42,666
And...

181
00:41:43,083 --> 00:41:45,711
And a ship would make 
a sweet trap, right?

182
00:41:46,003 --> 00:41:50,090
Confined space, metal 
walls, jail cell.

183
00:41:51,383 --> 00:41:52,593
Is cool, huh?

184
00:41:52,843 --> 00:41:54,553
Is it true half the 
people you meet

185
00:41:54,595 --> 00:41:56,305
