intelligence?

186
00:41:56,347 --> 00:41:59,141
Got to make sure the ship stays 
grounded when he comes for them, okay?

187
00:41:59,183 --> 00:42:00,935
Come on.

188
00:42:01,352 --> 00:42:04,230
Dahl, pull a node 
from the ship.

189
00:42:28,879 --> 00:42:30,005
I'll do it...

190
00:42:30,047 --> 00:42:31,131
Ooh!

191
00:42:31,173 --> 00:42:32,174
Ooh...

