And that ain't cool.

197
00:43:27,479 --> 00:43:30,858
Hey, I don't give a shit 
what they say. He's one guy.

198
00:43:33,235 --> 00:43:34,987
Whatever you say, man.

199
00:43:35,779 --> 00:43:37,489
He's one guy.

200
00:43:40,784 --> 00:43:41,994
Man...

201
00:43:52,755 --> 00:43:55,716
So I guess that's what passes for 
a fucking moon on this planet.

202
00:43:56,967 --> 00:43:59,094
It's gonna be a dark night.

203
00:43:59,636 --> 00:44:01,221
Advantage, him.

204
00:44:02,473 --> 00:44:06,560
Maybe he's gonna wear you down first. 
Force you to go without sleep.

205
00:44:06,602 --> 00:44:08,479
Can't you see I'm busy?

206
00:44:09,438 --> 00:44:11,565
I'm just sharing my thoughts.

207
00:44:11,607 --> 00:44:14,318
Well, now that you have,

208
00:44:15,986 --> 00:44:18,238
can I politely invite you to

209
00:44:18,322 --> 00:44:20,783
