a box, I will let you know.

213
00:44:55,192 --> 00:44:57,403
Grid 29D. Stand by, stand by.

214
00:45:02,491 --> 00:45:04,118
<i>What you got, cuz?</i>

215
00:45:05,994 --> 00:45:09,456
Aha, some dingo-dongo thing.

216
00:45:13,043 --> 00:45:15,546
Yeah. I see it now.

217
00:45:16,004 --> 00:45:17,131
<i>You want me to pop it?</i>

218
00:45:17,172 --> 00:45:19,758
