ripping shit off for salvage.

239
00:47:18,168 --> 00:47:19,670
Hey, Santana?

240
00:47:20,420 --> 00:47:22,923
You did sweep the area 
before I got here, right?

241
00:47:23,257 --> 00:47:25,008
