242
00:47:25,259 --> 00:47:27,511
<i>I just want to make sure 
no one has set any traps for us.</i>

243
00:47:27,553 --> 00:47:28,804
5Q.

244
00:47:31,765 --> 00:47:33,392
Understand what I'm saying?

245
00:47:33,559 --> 00:47:35,769
